---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Tagline from '../components/Tagline.astro';
---

<Layout title="Partnerships - Wellmade" description="We don't do subcontracting. We do partnerships. Your client is our client. Your reputation is our reputation.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="section-primary py-20 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-8">Partnerships</h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/80">
        We don't do subcontracting. We do partnerships.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/90 font-medium mt-4">
        The difference matters.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Difference -->
  <section class="section-light py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
        <div class="p-8 bg-light/50 rounded-2xl">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-body/60 mb-3">Subcontracting is:</h3>
          <p class="text-body text-lg">Here's a spec, build it, send the invoice.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8 bg-primary/10 rounded-2xl border-2 border-primary/20">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-primary mb-3">Partnership is:</h3>
          <p class="text-title text-lg font-medium">We're in this together. Your client is our client. Your reputation is our reputation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <section class="section-alt py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-8">How it works.</h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We integrate with your team. Not as a black box delivering code - as builders who understand your client, your context, your constraints.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We join calls when it makes sense. We challenge ideas when needed. We bring the craft - and sometimes the vision too.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-title font-medium">
        You stay in control of the relationship. We stay focused on the product.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Clear Roles -->
  <section class="section-light py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-8">Clear roles, mutual trust.</h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Good partnerships need clarity.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Who owns what. Who talks to whom. Who decides when there's disagreement.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-title font-medium">
        Get the RACI right and we're in. Skip it and we'll both regret it.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What We Bring -->
  <section class="section-primary py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-12">What we bring.</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-accent mb-2">Builders.</h3>
          <p class="text-white/70">Senior people who ship. No juniors learning on your client's budget.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-accent mb-2">Speed.</h3>
          <p class="text-white/70">AI-native methods mean we move fast without cutting corners.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-accent mb-2">Transparency.</h3>
          <p class="text-white/70">You'll always know where things stand.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-accent mb-2">Flexibility.</h3>
          <p class="text-white/70">Scale up, scale down. Project-based or ongoing.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What We Need -->
  <section class="section-light py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-12">What we need.</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-card">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Trust.</h3>
          <p class="text-body">Let us do what we're good at.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-card">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Access.</h3>
          <p class="text-body">To real context, real users when possible, real stakes.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-card">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">Honesty.</h3>
          <p class="text-body">If something's off, say it early.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Who We Work With -->
  <section class="section-alt py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-8">Who we work with.</h2>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Agencies. Studios. Consultancies. Innovation teams.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-body leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Anyone who needs builders but doesn't want to roll the dice on freelancers or fight with offshore teams.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-title font-medium">
        If you have the client and the vision, we have the craft.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section-light py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-title mb-6">Let's talk.</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-body mb-10">Every partnership starts with a conversation.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-primary text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors">
        Get in touch
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Tagline />
</Layout>
